Button.description: Button which sets placement mode, launches rocket and resets position

Mirror Mode.description: How the scene and camera is mirrored/flipped

Camera Pose.description: Pose mode of the tracked content

Anchor Camera Offset.description: Offset the target by this vector while its camera anchored

material.description: The material that the mesh uses

Mask.description: Occlude depth, do not render colors

resolution.title: Resolution
resolution.description: Resolution of one side of a cubemap. Use power of 2 resolution if you wish to use Mipmaps.

mipmaps.title: Mipmaps
mipmaps.description: If set to true, mipmaps will be allocated and autogenerated.

depth.title: Depth
depth.description: If set to true, depth buffer will be created.

Max Faces.description: The maximum number of faces the tracker will look for
